Vonda Phelps https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vonda_Phelps 0 Avonda Maude "Vonda" Phelps (April 19, 1915 – September 2, 2004) was an American child stage actress, vaudeville performer and dancer in the 1920s. She appeared in several silent film productions in 1922.
